Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:12.92,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Temp:\N Shinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.77,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:31.78,Bengoshi-Wood_Plaque,Plaque,0,0,0,,Hakamada \NLaw Office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.21,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:35.31,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Attorney: \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.41,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Hello, Hakamada Law Offices.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:38.95,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Yes, one moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.62,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Hello, Hakamada Law Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.58,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, we've got trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Shinozuka-san, the bread is done baking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:53.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,They're croissants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:56.79,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Never mind the croissants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.27,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,We're in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:00:59.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.04,Bengoshi-Wood_Plaque2,Plaque,0,0,0,,Hakamada \NLaw Office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.50,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,No one ever lines up at our office,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.15,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,but now there's a line of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Maybe they were lured by \Nthe aroma of my bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.81,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:15.22,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,They're clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.09,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,And phones have been \Nringing off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That can't be what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There's no way a crowd \Nlike this would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.17,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Excuse me, coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:25.66,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Excuse me, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.86,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Wow, what an amazing line!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:30.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Looks like it was effective, Kanae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.23,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san, do you know what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.30,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Let me in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.81,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Here, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.48,Bengoshi-Monthly_Monday,Mag,0,0,0,,Monthly Publication {\c&H613574&}Monday {D: I noticed this publication has been changed to "Manday" but it's probably a play on "Shonen Sunday" which is a classic publication of old}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.48,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Monthly Publication Monday, \Nhot off the press!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:49.02,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the monthly magazine \Nwith Kanae-san's syndication.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.45,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Kanae-chan's manga seems to be \Ngetting quite popular lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.39,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Hakamada's assistant: \NNonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.59,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Office landlord:\N Toyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.59,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I took advantage of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:03.06,Bengoshi-Compensation_Lawyer,Advertisement,0,0,0,,"Compensation Lawyer"{\c&H1C2618&\3c&H8F9E8D&} If you want a divorce and to get compensated, come to the Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:03.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,"If you want a divorce and to get compensated, \Ncome to the Hakamada Law Office."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:16.80,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N{\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:21.98,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption left,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Episode 5 \N Law Office of Hakamada in great peril?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Is that why they're all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:29.62,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,The advertisement was way\N more effective than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.93,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Sensei, you better get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:33.53,Bengoshi-Monthly_Monday2,Same mag,0,0,0,,Monthly Publication {\c&H191127}Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.20,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Rake in lots of compensation fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:37.24,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Ah, and I'll bill you for the ad later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.65,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.60,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Who is first in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.54,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.66,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.28,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:52.12,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Everyone, please wait a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.65,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.58,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,My name is Hakamada, attorney at law.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.05,Bengoshi-Top,Masayo,0,0,0,,I am Otsuka Masayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:02.79,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Client: \NOtsuka Masayo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.79,Bengoshi-Top,Masayo,0,0,0,,I'm a housewife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What can I do for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.44,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.19,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I can't forgive my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please relax, and give me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:31.08,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,My husband is cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.95,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Everyone. Please enjoy while you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.78,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.99,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Bread made by Hakamada-sensei himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.56,Default,Client1,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.57,Default,Client2,0,0,0,,Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.01,Default,Client3,0,0,0,,Sorry, can I have a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.12,Default,Clients4&5etc,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.24,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.32,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,He's been coming home late lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.65,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Sometimes after 7 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Do you consider that to be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:12.80,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,My husband is a public official, \Nhe works at a government office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:18.93,Bengoshi-Otsuka_Toru,Bubble,0,0,0,,Masayo's husband, public official: \NOtsuka Toru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.53,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,His work always ends at 5:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:19.27,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,so if he came straight home, \Nhe should be home by 6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.22,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,But, he comes home at 7:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.63,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,There's a gap of thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:28.68,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.66,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.76,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:42.03,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I have instructed my husband to report \Nto me his daily schedule and whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:45.19,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I check his cell phone \Nhistory every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.82,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I have set a GPS inside his briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:53.70,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I am always informed of his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.33,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What an oppressive ball and chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.12,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,It's perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.61,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I've been addicted lately to this \Nforeign drama, where I got the idea from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.08,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Iron Spy Woman Marilyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.08,Bengoshi-Spy_Marilyn,DVD box,0,0,0,,Iron Spy Woman \N{\fs25\c&HBDCAB6&\3c&H6E7367&}Marilyn
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.20,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,Commandant X,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.45,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,thank you for this amazing mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.12,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That show's getting popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.10,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,The result is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:21.41,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I have discovered my husband \Nis taking a ceramics class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:23.22,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,That's suspicious in itself, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.76,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,So I went to the ceramics class,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.37,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,and spied on him from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.79,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,And as I suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.08,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,The instructor is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.51,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Not only that, the woman's \Nhands and my husband's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:40.28,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,repeatedly touched each \Nother during the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.44,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Maybe she was showing \Nhim how to mold pottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.86,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,You can teach someone how to mold pottery \Nwithout touching each other's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.21,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.81,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't forgive my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:59.07,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,You can bill him for gobs \Nof compensation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When you say he's cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you referring to \Nthe touching of hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:10.17,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Otsuka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We cannot sue for compensation based on \Ntouching hands with the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.24,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There must be an illicit affair,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:21.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,which would be grounds for divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.69,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Otherwise it would be impossible \Nto get approval for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:30.86,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Can you give me a concrete \Ndefinition of "illicit affair"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.19,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Simply put, that would be "sex."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.41,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Se-Se-Sex?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Otsuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Otsuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.23,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Wouldn't {\i1}that {\i0}be grounds \Nfor a death sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:47.17,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Who decided that an illicit \Naffair has to be sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:51.31,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,As far as I'm concerned, touching hands \Nwith the opposite sex is illicit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It has already been determined by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:58.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It would be difficult to sue for \Ncompensation based on your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.66,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,You're changing the storyline, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The storyline?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:08.29,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,This manga character is \Nyou, isn't it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.83,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Look what it says here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.24,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Is it a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:15.43,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble,Bubble,0,0,0,,"There is no compensation \Nfee I cannot get for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,"There is no compensation \Nfee I cannot get for you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.40,Default,People in line,0,0,0,,Water. Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.45,Default,Client,0,0,0,,Why did you give us that to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:29.38,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei had good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, may I see you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.25,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:39.06,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This is the main \Nprotagonist's catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.06,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But I've never said \Nanything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:46.52,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Well, actually, the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.90,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,We got the results for \NFebruary's reader votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.38,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,You're 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.47,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,Amazing! I'm in the top ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.13,Bengoshi-Flashback_Top,Misato,0,0,0,,That's no ranking to be happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.17,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Editor at Tokiwa Publishing: \NTabata Misato
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:59.84,Bengoshi-Flashback_Top,Misato,0,0,0,,You're 9th in popularity \Nout of eleven syndications.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.66,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.43,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,If you continue flying \Nunder the radar like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.88,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,you could potentially get canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.23,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:13.01,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,The reader poll rates your \Nstory contents highly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:18.06,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,but the majority of comments said \Nthe leading character is too plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:22.56,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,I think he needs to have some kind \Nof quality that attracts the readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.77,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,An attractive quality?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.20,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,For example, the protagonist \Nshould have a cool catchphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.21,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,A catchphrase... for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:34.77,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,Like, "If you have any sympathy, \Ngive me compensation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.88,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,That one sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:42.64,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,Then how about, "I won't die \Nuntil I get compensated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.52,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,What kind of situation \Nwould that apply to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.83,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,"I'll pay the entire\N compensation back to you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.80,Bengoshi-Flashback,Kanae,0,0,0,,Why would he pay back the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.42,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,You are completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.51,Bengoshi-Flashback,Misato,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.06,Bengoshi-Credits_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Cafe waitress:\NMizutani Sara
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.05,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,"There is no compensation \Nfee I cannot get for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:03.44,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,There is no other suitable \Ncatchphrase for your protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:07.27,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,The manga popularity will rise \Nwith it, there is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You applied the waitress's \Nsuggestion literally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:15.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,She both seems to be and not be \Nsome kind of spiritual medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:18.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't you think a person like that \Nwould be nothing but suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.31,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's \Na pretty good catchphrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.82,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,"There is no compensation fee I \Ncannot get for you" isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,A lawyer must not \Nguarantee specific results.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So that's why there's \Na crowd out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.09,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,What's the story, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.28,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,You will get me compensation, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:39.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Based on your situation, I \Ndon't think it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:46.24,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,That means this is false advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.24,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble2,Bubble,0,0,0,,"There is no compensation \Nfee I cannot get for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.07,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I will report this to the \Nappropriate authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.33,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,and they will take appropriate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:56.23,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I will contact the publisher \Nof this manga, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, no, please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:58.66,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Because Sensei can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:00.79,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.40,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei is a professional \Nin lawsuit compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:10.00,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He will assuredly produce satisfactory \Nresults for you, regardless of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.15,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,So, it's true then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, can I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,A lawyer mustn't guarantee \Na specific result.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's a crucial time for me, \Nmy syndication just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.62,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,If some weird claim gets associated \Nwith it, it'll quickly get canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.57,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Even if you can't get compensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:31.44,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,isn't there some way you \Ncan satisfy the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But what's impossible is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.19,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You haven't paid me yet \Nfor last month's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.06,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:38.93,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:43.03,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I can contact the appropriate authorities\N and have them take appropriate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.21,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.65,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.24,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:57.06,Default,Client1,0,0,0,,Um, when can we get legal counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you will have \Nto wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.20,Default,Client2,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to eat \Nthis strange, awful bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.84,Default,Client3,0,0,0,,We should go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.38,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,One moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.59,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I will introduce you to him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.77,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kanae,0,0,0,,He's still talking to a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.51,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,If the people leave, I paid for \Nthe advertisement for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.90,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,We just have to listen to what they've got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.39,Bengoshi-Overlap,Ka,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:20.53,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei can have \Nthe final word, but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:24.09,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,we have divorce experience ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.32,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.34,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Kanae-chan, you have \Nexperience with divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:31.17,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Use it as reference,\N and hear them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.03,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Next in line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.68,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.39,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,The rest of you, please wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.79,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Outside_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.71,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,She is cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.50,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,So, I want compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.79,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,When did she start cheating on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.97,Bengoshi-Credits_Oyama,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Client:\N Oyama Takayuki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:51.38,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,A friend of mine witnessed it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.27,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,about two months ago, \Nand told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:00.07,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I was told Aya was flirting \Nand walking with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:12:07.81,Bengoshi-Inui_Aya,Bubble,0,0,0,,Takayuki's lover \NInui Aya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.06,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This has been going on\N for two months now, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.81,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.23,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,My other friends have \Nseen things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.42,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I asked them what they saw, and \Nit seems she's with different men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.82,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,She's not only seeing two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.72,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,there are maybe three or four other men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.83,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,By the way, are you \Nplanning on divorcing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.25,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.40,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,No, we're not even married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.57,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.90,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I'm only in high school, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.86,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,High school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.07,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,And who is this Aya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.54,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,She's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.78,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,We've been going out for almost a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.09,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:44.38,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, our client is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:46.95,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.70,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want \Nme to call you "Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.35,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I might not look it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.76,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,but I was once a tutor \Nfor my friend's kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.00,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,So the "Sensei" part isn't false.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.79,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Now, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.50,Bengoshi-Credits,Client,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Client:\NSawada Chiharu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.64,Bengoshi-Top,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I think my husband is cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.58,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:10.31,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What, may I ask, is your \Nhusband's profession?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.13,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,He's a high school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:20.55,Bengoshi-Sawada_Shuji,Bubble,0,0,0,,{\a1}Chiharu's husband, high school teacher: \NSawada Shuji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:16.45,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,It must fall into the forbidden pattern \Nof the teacher-student love affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:20.55,Bengoshi-Top,Chiharu,0,0,0,,No, it's not with a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.69,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Oh. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.69,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.22,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Ah, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.30,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,So, who is the partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.10,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:38.37,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Two weeks ago I coincidentally \Nsaw my husband in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:41.08,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,It was at a place far from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.34,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,It bothered me so I followed him.
