Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.45,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Where's the partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.78,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,That's the partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.92,Bengoshi-Binbin,Sign,0,0,0,,Rock Hard \NSchool
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:58.66,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,My husband is addicted to sex clubs.
