Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.93,Default,People,0,0,0,,How long must we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:17.29,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,After work, my husband often \Nbrings flowers home for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Sounds to me like a nice husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.00,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,What's so nice about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.47,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,He's interested in the young \Nand cute flower shop girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:28.38,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I have witnessed my husband \Npurchasing flowers once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.50,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,He had a lecherous look on his face \Nwhile she picked flowers for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:37.48,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I counted it, he looked \Ninto her eyes seven times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:44.40,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,That could lead to adultery \Nin a big way, couldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say that wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.62,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,One time I saw a tag on \Nthe flowers he brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.41,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,It said "jealous" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.05,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,That note was meant to challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.03,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,It was a message from \Nthat flower shop girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:01.51,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,that she is jealous of me and \Nmy husband's relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:06.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, those tags are poetic\N descriptions of varieties of flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.25,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Oh yes, and another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.09,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I inspected his briefcase \Nthe other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:12.40,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,and there was a handcuff \Nand eye-mask in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:18.29,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,My husband is entering \Nthe world of S&M!
