Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.49,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.30,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, aren't you done with her yet?
