Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:43.06,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,We didn't want to keep the clients \Nwaiting, so we took to counseling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't take that \Nkind of initiative!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:48.01,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When a person poses to be \Na lawyer and gives counsel,
