Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:56.24,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,Caption bottom,0,0,0,,{\fad(590,0)}When a non-lawyer gives legal counsel for the purpose of obtaining fees
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.12,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it's called unauthorized counsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.42,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You could get arrested for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.16,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:56.24,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,We were just taking down client \Ninformation for you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.00,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Can compensation be gotten in \Nthe case of a dating couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.90,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Do sex clubs fall in the \Ncategory of adultery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.38,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Can you get compensated by them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I don't want to say I can't, but...
