Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:08.95,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Maybe there won't be a monetary payoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:13.67,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What, there won't be a monetary payoff?
