Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:45.78,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:49.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Frequenting sex clubs is an \Noutstandingly illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:53.90,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I've had several cases in the past of \Ncompensation lawsuits on those grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.27,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:56.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,when is the last time you \Nhad sex with your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.91,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, how could you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:04.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's often the case that when husbands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:07.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,begin frequenting sex clubs, \Nmarriages become sexless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:12.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If we can prove his illicit activity of \Nsex clubs and that your marriage is sexless,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that would beef up the \Ncompensation fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When was the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:20.60,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,The day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:23.74,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Huh? That's quite recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:27.17,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,We do it at least twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:29.24,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That's quite feisty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In that case, please \Nrecall in fine detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,For example, ever since he started \Nfrequenting hostess clubs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:37.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,foreplay has become sloppy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:39.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,or he has become naughtier...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.31,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Is there any little change\N you can think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:48.25,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:49.31,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You seem to be enthused all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:51.21,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You were so reluctant at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.19,0:23:55.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I acknowledge everyone's \Nwillingness to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:57.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm only responding accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.33,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:05.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Hello, Hakamada speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:10.41,Bengoshi-Credits_Toru,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Masayo's husband:\N Otsuka Toru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:08.34,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It's Umemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.13,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm currently tailing Otsuka\N Masayo-san's husband, Toru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:13.00,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,He seems to be on his way to the flower \Nshop, toward his alleged adulterous partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:15.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Have you captured any \Nevidence of adultery?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:17.82,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:22.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Even for you, investigating for three \Npeople at once must be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.09,0:24:24.03,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.03,0:24:25.90,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,In season 6 episode 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:28.24,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Marilyn did background checks on \Neighteen people simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:30.50,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Compared to that, this is a cinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:32.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'll leave it in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:34.86,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I've got some noteworthy \Ninformation, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:36.48,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I sent you an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.48,0:24:39.47,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm continuing my pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:42.61,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Vertical_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada \NLaw Office
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:47.87,Bengoshi-Subject,Inbox1,0,0,0,,Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:47.87,Bengoshi-Senders,Inbox1,0,0,0,,Umemoto Kurumi \N\N{\c&H806F50&} Breadmaker Crafts\N\N Yuasa Pantry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:47.87,Bengoshi-Senders,Inbox1,0,0,0,,{\a3}Interim investigation report \N\N{\c&H756E4E&}"Bread baking correspondence course" \N\NYour item has been shipped
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:53.15,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,What has my husband been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:55.73,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,The GPS is showing \Nhe's all over the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.73,0:24:59.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It appears he's taking full \Nadvantage of his freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.66,0:25:03.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I should have plenty of evidence soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.23,0:25:04.71,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.74,0:25:11.17,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Sensei. I proposed to her like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:14.20,Bengoshi-Text_Messages,Takayuki text,0,0,0,,{\3c&H349C76&}I've been thinking I want to marry you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:14.20,Bengoshi-Text_Messages,Aya text,0,0,0,,{\a11}I appreciate the sentiment, \Nbut you don't have to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.46,0:25:14.20,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,She turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.31,0:25:17.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.57,0:25:21.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have no problem if we have \Nproof that you want to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:23.29,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.34,0:25:26.70,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.70,0:25:29.22,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Did you find out anything \Nabout my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.98,0:25:31.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:34.49,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,An outstanding investigator is \Ncurrently investigating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:37.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I think we will have \Nevidence quite soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:39.32,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.82,0:26:07.02,Bengoshi-Wood_Plaque2,Plaque,0,0,0,,Hakamada\N Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.45,0:26:10.44,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Are you here for legal counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.58,0:26:11.44,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:14.01,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How long have you been waiting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.34,0:26:16.34,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Since 8:30 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.34,0:26:17.87,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.87,0:26:18.90,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,We will get to you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.90,0:26:22.23,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can wait till \Nthe others are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.23,0:26:24.71,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,My case isn't a big deal, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.10,0:26:29.12,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sensei is just kneading \Nbread dough right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:32.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:34.99,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, we have another client.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.99,0:26:35.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:38.87,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,She has been here since early morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.26,0:26:41.20,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.26,0:26:45.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood, please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.53,0:26:46.91,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.41,0:26:52.87,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.67,0:27:00.84,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Client:\N Kumagai Setsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.41,0:27:03.93,Bengoshi-Top,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I've been married to my \Nhusband for fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.88,0:27:09.45,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Our marriage had been arranged \Nby both our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.45,0:27:11.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Everyone, please don't eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.97,0:27:14.69,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Lawyers are sworn to client \Nconfidentiality, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.69,0:27:16.85,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Come on, lighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.85,0:27:19.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san, when did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.18,0:27:20.67,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.67,0:27:23.33,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I live for gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.33,0:27:26.73,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Don't take it away from me, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.73,0:27:30.71,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,My husband's partner is a friend \Nof his from back in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.38,0:27:37.18,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,My husband has introduced me to her, \Nand I've seen her several times since.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.23,0:27:41.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So, when did your \Nhusband's adultery begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.70,0:27:44.08,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.19,0:27:47.69,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,from before we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.69,0:27:48.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.02,0:27:51.36,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:55.74,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,He had been seeing her \Nbefore we were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.31,0:27:59.96,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,It appears the relationship still \Ncontinued after our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.96,0:28:03.11,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Adultery for fifteen years, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.46,0:28:06.41,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,This is quite a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.98,0:28:10.21,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Maybe it's worth more than \Nten million in compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.21,0:28:11.37,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.37,0:28:13.60,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Ten million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.60,0:28:18.81,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Their secret trysts are perhaps \Nonce or twice a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.16,0:28:22.52,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,His partner has a husband as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:25.78,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,A double-adultery to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.78,0:28:27.97,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,This is a big fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.57,0:28:30.50,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Don't lose it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.50,0:28:33.19,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That's enough, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.19,0:28:36.65,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,So you say, but you're \Npulling me so weakly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.65,0:28:38.40,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You want to eavesdrop, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.78,0:28:41.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,How much compensation \Nare you hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.55,0:28:44.03,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,For compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.54,0:28:47.68,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I want nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.65,0:28:51.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You do plan to divorce him, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.78,0:28:53.84,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:57.19,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I have no intention of divorcing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.89,0:29:03.01,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,It's laughable, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.33,0:29:08.96,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,but, I love my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.69,0:29:13.04,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,My husband is a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.20,0:29:19.54,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,We talk a lot over dinner every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.58,0:29:23.11,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,We travel a lot together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.11,0:29:26.05,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I have many fond memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.38,0:29:29.25,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,If I were to divorce him,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.25,0:29:31.72,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,it would be tantamount to \Nthrowing everything away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.87,0:29:36.43,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Those memories will turn into regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.71,0:29:43.00,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I absolutely wouldn't \Nwant that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.48,0:29:49.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What then is it you want, Kumagai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.27,0:29:53.74,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.70,0:30:00.48,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,is for my husband to stop \Nseeing the other woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.87,0:30:03.68,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.83,0:30:08.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.63,0:30:14.68,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I will send a notice within a few days to\N your husband's adulterous partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.68,0:30:19.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I will state that there are grounds \Nfor lawsuit compensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.29,0:30:23.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but if the adulterous \Nrelationship were to stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.37,0:30:25.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,compensation will not be pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.51,0:30:28.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Since she is married as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.53,0:30:30.77,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'd want to \Nprotect her own household.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.12,0:30:34.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I will probably get her quick consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:39.60,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Sensei, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.42,0:30:42.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You can thank me when \Neverything works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.54,0:30:46.36,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't \Nwant compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.26,0:30:48.30,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.86,0:30:52.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.86,0:31:09.12,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.12,0:31:13.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I've made preparation to take a bundle\N in compensation from your hateful partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.60,0:31:15.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let me explain your respective strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.37,0:31:17.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Who should I start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.61,0:31:23.37,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Please go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.37,0:31:25.75,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,No, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:30.47,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Otsuka-san was here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.43,0:31:32.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:34.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:40.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.76,0:31:47.35,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to give \Nit a little more thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.35,0:31:48.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.42,0:31:52.01,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I think I want to do that too, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.01,0:31:53.15,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.15,0:31:55.00,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.49,0:31:57.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.06,0:32:01.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We've got plenty evidence, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.24,0:32:06.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,These are photos of \NOtsuka-san's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.83,0:32:09.57,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When he was freed of his shackles,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.57,0:32:12.38,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,he seems to have enjoyed his freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:14.07,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,At the flower shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.07,0:32:15.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,At the ceramics class.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.87,0:32:19.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There were cute ladies present \Nin both establishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.46,0:32:23.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Our investigator spoke \Nwith both those women.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.59,0:32:26.74,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And it seems your husband goes to those \Nplaces based on dubious pretexts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.74,0:32:32.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Masayo-san, you and your husband \Nare having a ten year anniversary, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.30,0:32:35.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's been telling those women,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.26,0:32:38.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that he's preparing \Nsecret gifts for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.64,0:32:40.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,At the flower shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.67,0:32:43.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,he said he was going to choose \Nhis own flower bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.92,0:32:45.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,At the ceramics class,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:47.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,he said he was going to make \Noriginal his-and-her teacups.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.53,0:32:50.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,As to the handcuff and eye-mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.63,0:32:54.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it seems he was going to perform some kind of \Nmagic trick to surprise you on your anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.85,0:32:59.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Supposedly, he wants to show you how \Nmuch he appreciates your watching over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.53,0:33:03.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Pretexts like that are quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.67,0:33:05.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's a way of appealing to \Npartners, letting them know
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.92,0:33:08.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,they're married, so all \Nthey want is to be lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.22,0:33:13.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What a devious husband he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.77,0:33:19.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Next, Oyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.76,0:33:26.28,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Our investigator sent these photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.28,0:33:27.37,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.02,0:33:30.17,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,An obstetrics clinic...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.02,0:33:31.75,Bengoshi-Obsterics_Clinic,Sign in photo,0,0,0,,Obstetrics Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.17,0:33:33.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It seems Aya-san \Nhas a child in her womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.85,0:33:35.15,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:40.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,According to investigation, she's \Nbeen pregnant for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.37,0:33:44.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, then again, who knows \Nwhose baby it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.67,0:33:47.54,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And it seems she's going \Nto have the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.54,0:33:51.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,To save up for raising the child, she \Nstarted working at a hostess club.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.84,0:33:56.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She's quite dandy, and is popular \Nwith the customers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.35,0:33:59.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I hear her job is to accompany those \Ncustomers out to town, and quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.77,0:34:02.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Accompany...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.97,0:34:04.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So it seems quite clear now,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.84,0:34:08.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that she's been wanting \Nto marry you for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.27,0:34:12.20,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now, we can easily prove that \Nshe's made a breach of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.56,0:34:15.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And Sawada-san, regarding your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.98,0:34:20.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He went straightway to the \Nestablishment after school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.30,0:34:22.40,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Look how crisp the photo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.40,0:34:25.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This is sufficient evidence \Nfor illicit activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.07,0:34:29.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,However, there's one thing \NI need to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.90,0:34:35.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The establishment your husband went to \Nwas not the sex club on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.34,0:34:40.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He went to the establishment with \Na gay clientele, on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.78,0:34:39.38,Bengoshi-Gay_Bar,Photo sign,0,0,0,,Gay Bar \N{\b1}Me and My Bro{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.35,0:34:42.21,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.21,0:34:44.16,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:45.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.33,0:34:47.15,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,as confirmed by the establishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.15,0:34:52.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,your husband would select a young \Nman there, who was a former student of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.75,0:34:56.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,They said he was never \Nthere to enjoy himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.16,0:34:58.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but would talk to the young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.83,0:35:01.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,trying to convince him of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,They said he was trying to find the \Nyoung man another place of employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.53,0:35:07.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The people at the establishment \Nfind your husband to be a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.95,0:35:11.66,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Anyway, who cares why \Nhe goes to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:15.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have this photo, which \Nis sufficient evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:21.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Now, who wants to\N start their case first?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.86,0:35:36.62,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I'm going home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.26,0:35:39.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:44.13,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Today is our ten-year anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.75,0:35:48.40,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I should have a present \Nready for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.34,0:35:53.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But maybe your husband \Ndidn't get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.34,0:35:56.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's all a pretext to meet with\N those female employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.52,0:35:58.48,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,He's not that kind of man!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.94,0:36:02.56,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.05,0:36:05.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.18,0:36:08.41,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.21,0:36:11.35,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I owe her an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.06,0:36:13.44,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.44,0:36:15.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She's the one that should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.22,0:36:20.45,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,The baby she's carrying... is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.45,0:36:24.46,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You can't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.46,0:36:27.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She's been seen with many \Ndifferent men, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.29,0:36:29.07,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Aya isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.56,0:36:33.06,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:36.13,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.94,0:36:39.36,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,I should've said I wanted to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.95,0:36:42.67,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,She wouldn't have had to \Ngo work at a hostess club.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.67,0:36:45.55,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,So I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.54,0:36:49.24,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,going to propose to her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.76,0:36:53.04,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,And of course, I'll look for a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.90,0:36:59.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.50,0:37:04.66,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I'll be going home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:06.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.75,0:37:13.18,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,The boy who works at that establishment \Nwas an outstanding student.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:16.11,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,My husband had high hopes for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.42,0:37:22.68,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I think my husband was trying\N to free him from the sex industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.68,0:37:27.31,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,and find him legitimate employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.90,0:37:29.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.33,0:37:32.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's probably a closet homosexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.19,0:37:33.72,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.11,0:37:38.95,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I told you my husband and\N I have frequent intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.71,0:37:44.55,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I said it was the day before \Nyesterday when we did it last...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.33,0:37:48.80,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,But we did it last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.37,0:37:55.16,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,He must be shouldering \Nconcern for his student.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.62,0:37:59.59,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,He was more intense with me than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.61,0:38:05.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.62,0:38:10.52,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I know I'm overstepping my bounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.93,0:38:12.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but all of you are foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:17.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You have {\i1}me{\i0} as your \Nlegal representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.41,0:38:20.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There is no compensation \Nfee I cannot get for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.43,0:38:30.31,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you all telling me, that you \Nwant something more than money?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.81,0:38:33.91,Default,Masayo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.95,0:38:35.91,Default,Takayuki,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.91,0:38:37.88,Default,Chiharu,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.62,0:38:40.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:44.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, that's that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.69,0:38:51.96,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Sign_Night,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.32,0:38:54.56,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.56,0:38:56.68,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Good work, Umemoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.68,0:38:57.40,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.40,0:38:59.55,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,That was a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.55,0:39:00.83,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.83,0:39:06.14,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I kept pursuing those targets, \Nand took these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.94,0:39:47.82,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, did you know it was going to \Nturn out like this from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.55,0:39:51.18,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:56.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I just gave everyone the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.03,0:39:59.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, as to how they would \Nprocess those facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.65,0:40:01.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,it was entirely up to the clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.90,0:40:05.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Before you start basking in your glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.57,0:40:08.23,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,you owe me for the investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:09.44,Bengoshi-Invoice,Letter,0,0,0,,Invoice
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:10.60,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.60,0:40:13.17,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You said you were going to \Nfoot the bill, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.17,0:40:16.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, can you please wait a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.09,0:40:17.28,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.28,0:40:20.62,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You should've made a bundle \Nwith all those clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:23.74,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I didn't make any money \Nfrom the clients today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.74,0:40:25.72,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Because counseling is free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.72,0:40:28.65,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much hardship \Nwe're having because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.65,0:40:31.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I assure you, I will pay \Nyou at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.08,0:40:34.72,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Here's the bill for the \Nad in the manga mag.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.72,0:40:36.50,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'll leave this to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.49,0:40:47.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I received an official reply \Nfrom your husband's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.81,0:40:49.90,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She consented to the term in the notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.90,0:40:53.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and will call off her \Nrelationship with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.29,0:41:00.92,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,Sensei, I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.84,0:41:03.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.35,0:41:11.73,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have asked a lawyer\N to step in to ask for her to call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.73,0:41:15.36,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, it's an unusual case,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.78,0:41:18.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but there are many ways \NI can be of assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.36,0:41:22.69,Default,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I don't know much about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.50,0:41:27.39,Bengoshi-Top,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I've asked other lawyers in the \Npast, and they all turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:31.54,Bengoshi-Top,Setsuko,0,0,0,,You have taken on an \Nunreasonable request.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.54,0:41:33.63,Bengoshi-Top,Setsuko,0,0,0,,I am truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.85,0:41:36.63,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.22,0:41:41.34,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I never turn down anyone \Nwho is truly in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.37,0:41:52.47,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Hey, did you drop the catchphrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.47,0:41:55.14,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Where he says, "There is no \Ncompensation fee I cannot get for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.14,0:41:56.29,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.29,0:41:59.28,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,The protagonist's \Ncatchphrase is now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.28,0:42:00.18,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.18,0:42:03.88,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,"I never turn down anyone \Nwho is truly in need."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.14,0:42:03.88,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble3,Bubble,0,0,0,,I never turn down anyone \Nwho is truly in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:08.22,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I think this catchphrase \Nsuits the protagonist better.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.22,0:42:10.13,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,I think it's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.13,0:42:10.86,Bengoshi-Top,Misato,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.86,0:42:15.23,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,There can be no other \Ncatchphrase for this protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:22.20,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,She changes what she says \Nfrom one minute to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.20,0:42:27.84,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble3,Bubble,0,0,0,,I never turn down anyone\N who is truly in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.84,0:42:29.88,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.84,0:42:39.35,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.88,0:42:31.81,Bengoshi-Top,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey Yukio, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.17,0:42:34.68,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,His client is his long lost father!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.17,0:42:34.68,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,They meet again after 30 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.81,0:42:35.41,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That person is the most \Ndisreputable person in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.74,0:42:39.35,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\c&H27E5D6&}Hakamada's younger sister's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:37.53,Bengoshi-Top,Sister,0,0,0,,My father is being tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.28,0:42:39.35,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,{\c&H790AE2&}To settle the feud between father and child!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.53,0:42:39.02,Bengoshi-Top,Voice,0,0,0,,Please protect your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.02,0:42:40.62,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That man is not my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.38,0:42:42.82,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}This drama is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.62,0:42:42.80,Bengoshi-Top,Voice,0,0,0,,Why must you be so obstinate?

